00:22:58.570 --> 00:23:01.040
that there's substantial
reliance on these exemptions

00:23:01.040 --> 00:23:03.420
in pretty big institutions.

00:23:03.420 --> 00:23:04.720
You know, at this point,

00:23:04.720 --> 00:23:08.760
the educational exemption has been
granted and renewed for long enough

00:23:08.760 --> 00:23:10.660
that we've-- you know,
at universities,

00:23:10.660 --> 00:23:14.830 position:56%
