00:23:22.970 --> 00:23:25.940
So in three years,
that's almost $100,000,

00:23:25.940 --> 00:23:29.300
where the hope every time we
buy that DVD is that faculty

00:23:29.300 --> 00:23:34.320
and students can make lawful uses
in accord with the exemption.

00:23:34.320 --> 00:23:37.570
So, that's another great reason
