00:23:47.020 --> 00:23:48.320
&gt;&gt; Brandon Butler: Oh, absolutely.

00:23:48.320 --> 00:23:49.620
&gt;&gt; Regan Smith: But the reason
I ask is that, you know,

00:23:49.620 --> 00:23:50.990
Congress is pretty clear
