00:23:50.990 --> 00:23:54.590
to be a failsafe mechanism that
it's intended to allow the Office

00:23:54.590 --> 00:23:58.420 position:56%
to keep their pulse on technological
developments and react.

00:23:58.420 --> 00:24:00.660
And so, it cuts both ways,

00:24:00.660 --> 00:24:03.180
that an exemption granted
might become ossified

00:24:03.180 --> 00:24:05.340
or overtaken by market events.

00:24:05.340 --> 00:24:06.640
&gt;&gt; Brandon Butler: Yeah.

00:24:06.640 --> 00:24:07.940
No, I mean, make no mistake,

00:24:07.940 --> 00:24:09.240
this is sort of a third
best solution, right?

00:24:09.240 --> 00:24:11.730
First best is the Unlocking
Technology Act.

00:24:11.730 --> 00:24:14.040
Second best is a permanent
exemption.

00:24:14.040 --> 00:24:15.750
But third best is a renewal.

00:24:15.750 --> 00:24:18.490
And I agree that the
concerns that educators have

00:24:18.490 --> 00:24:23.220
in particular don't tend to
actually become overtaken.

00:24:23.220 --> 00:24:29.520
So for example, VHS tapes, there
