always retains the ability to go

01:11:20.020 --> 01:11:26.010
to court and hash that out and win
either on contributory infringement

01:11:26.010 --> 01:11:29.030
or infringement, depending
on what the activity is.

01:11:29.030 --> 01:11:33.650
And that would end the
exemption and end it next time,

01:11:33.650 --> 01:11:36.290
whereas if you lose, you
just don't get that chance.

01:11:36.290 --> 01:11:40.880
So, it's structurally
unequal in a way

01:11:40.880 --> 01:11:43.790
that makes mirror image
treatment inappropriate.

01:11:43.790 --> 01:11:45.650
