01:12:08.520 --> 01:12:10.340
down with other things doesn't mean

01:12:10.340 --> 01:12:13.320
that the initial exemption
was inappropriate,

01:12:13.320 --> 01:12:16.280
even though in some
sense, it's been rejected.

01:12:16.280 --> 01:12:19.380
And I think the kind of
line-drawing that you would end

01:12:19.380 --> 01:12:24.540
up doing would be contrary to
the goal of simplifying things.

01:12:24.540 --> 01:12:25.840
&gt;&gt; Regan Smith: Thank you.

